#: ../../topics/system/intro.rst:2
msgid "SCQL System Overview"
msgstr "SCQL 系统概述"

#: ../../topics/system/intro.rst:4
msgid ""
"Secure Collaborative Query Language (SCQL) is a system that allows "
"multiple distrusting parties to run joint analysis without revealing "
"their private data."
msgstr ""
"安全协作查询语言（Secure Collaborative Query Language， "
"SCQL）是一个允许多个互不信任参与方在不泄露各自隐私数据的条件下进行联合数据分析的系统。"

#: ../../topics/system/intro.rst:7
msgid "Key Features"
msgstr "关键特点"

#: ../../topics/system/intro.rst:9
msgid "Semi-honest security. SCQL assumes that all parties are semi-honest."
msgstr "半诚实安全。SCQL 假设所有参与方都是半诚实的。"

#: ../../topics/system/intro.rst:10
msgid "Support multiple parties (N >= 1)."
msgstr "支持多方（N>=1）。"

#: ../../topics/system/intro.rst:11
msgid ""
"Support common SQL select syntax and functions to meet the needs of most "
"scenarios. Please check :doc:`/reference/implementation-status` for "
"details."
msgstr ""
"支持常见的 SQL select 语法和函数，满足大多数场景的需求。详情请查看 :doc:`/reference/implementation-"
"status`。"

#: ../../topics/system/intro.rst:12
msgid ""
"Practical performance. SCQL has multiple levels of performance "
"optimization."
msgstr "实用的性能。SCQL 具有多层次的性能优化。"

#: ../../topics/system/intro.rst:13
msgid "Simple structure, easy to integrate."
msgstr "结构简单，易于集成。"

#: ../../topics/system/intro.rst:16
msgid "Architecture"
msgstr "架构"

#: ../../topics/system/intro.rst:18
msgid "SCQL uses a compiler + engine architecture:"
msgstr "SCQL 使用编译器 + 引擎架构："

#: ../../topics/system/intro.rst:20
msgid ""
"**Compiler** translates SQL queries into secure execution plans. The "
"compiler performs query parsing, logical planning, and generates "
"execution graphs that specify how data should be processed securely."
msgstr "**编译器** 将 SQL 查询转换为安全执行计划。编译器执行查询解析、逻辑规划，并生成指定如何安全处理数据的执行图。"

#: ../../topics/system/intro.rst:21
msgid ""
"**SCQLEngine** is a hybrid MPC-plaintext execution engine that executes "
"the plans generated by the compiler. SCQLEngine collaborates with peer "
"engines to run the execution graph and returns query results. SCQLEngine "
"is implemented on top of state-of-the-art MPC framework "
"`secretflow/spu`_."
msgstr ""
"**SCQLEngine** 是一个明密文混合执行引擎，执行编译器生成的计划。SCQLEngine "
"与对等引擎协作运行执行图并返回查询结果。SCQLEngine 基于先进的 MPC 框架 `secretflow/spu`_ 实现。"

#: ../../topics/system/intro.rst:24
msgid "How SCQL Works"
msgstr "SCQL 如何工作"

#: ../../topics/system/intro.rst:26
msgid ""
"We will show how SCQL works through the life of the following sample SCQL"
" query Q."
msgstr "我们将通过以下的 SCQL 查询样本 Q 的整个生命周期来展示 SCQL 是如何工作的。"

#: ../../topics/system/intro.rst:28
msgid "SCQL query Q"
msgstr "SCQL 查询 Q"

#: ../../topics/system/intro.rst:38 ../../topics/system/intro.rst:42
msgid "Table schema"
msgstr "表的结构"

#: ../../topics/system/intro.rst:40
msgid "Let's have a look at the schema of tables involved in the above query Q."
msgstr "让我们来看看上面查询 Q 中涉及的表的结构。"

#: ../../topics/system/intro.rst:45
msgid "``bank_1``"
msgstr "``bank_1``"

#: ../../topics/system/intro.rst:46
msgid ""
"Party Bank1 owns the table ``bank_1`` in its local database ``DB1``, "
"which has two columns ``customer_id`` and ``deposit``."
msgstr ""
"参与方 Bank1 在其本地数据库 ``DB1`` 中有张表 ``bank_1``，该数据表有两列分别是 ``customer_id`` 和 "
"``deposit``。"

#: ../../topics/system/intro.rst:47
msgid "``bank_2``"
msgstr "``bank_2``"

#: ../../topics/system/intro.rst:48
msgid ""
"Party Bank2 owns the table ``bank_2`` in its local database ``DB2``, "
"which has two columns ``customer_id`` and ``loan``."
msgstr ""
"参与方 Bank2 在其本地数据库 ``DB2`` 中有张表 ``bank_2``，该数据表有两列分别是 ``customer_id`` 和 "
"``loan``。"

#: ../../topics/system/intro.rst:52
msgid "Lifetime of SCQL query"
msgstr "SCQL 查询的生命周期"

#: ../../topics/system/intro.rst:54
msgid "SCQL Workflow"
msgstr "SCQL 工作流"

#: ../../topics/system/intro.rst:58
msgid "Step1. Compile SQL Query"
msgstr "步骤1. 编译 SQL 查询"

#: ../../topics/system/intro.rst:60
msgid "The compiler receives the SQL query and performs the following operations:"
msgstr "编译器接收 SQL 查询并执行以下操作："

#: ../../topics/system/intro.rst:62
msgid "**Step1.1 Parse**"
msgstr "**步骤1.1 解析**"

#: ../../topics/system/intro.rst:64
msgid "Parser parses the SQL query Q into an AST (Abstract Syntax Tree)."
msgstr "解析器将 SQL 查询 Q 解析为 AST（抽象语法树）。"

#: ../../topics/system/intro.rst:66
msgid "**Step1.2 Plan**"
msgstr "**步骤1.2 规划**"

#: ../../topics/system/intro.rst:68
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Planner converts the AST into Logical Plan, and applies optimizations to "
"the plan."
msgstr "规划器将 AST 转换为逻辑计划，并且对逻辑计划进行优化。"

#: ../../topics/system/intro.rst:70
msgid "Logical Plan for Q"
msgstr "Q 的逻辑计划"

#: ../../topics/system/intro.rst:74
#, fuzzy
msgid "**Step1.3 Translate to Operator Graph**"
msgstr "**步骤1.3 转化成操作图**"

#: ../../topics/system/intro.rst:76
#, fuzzy
msgid "The compiler translates the logical plan into an operator graph"
msgstr "编译器将逻辑计划转换为查询 Q 的操作图。"

#: ../../topics/system/intro.rst:78
#, fuzzy
msgid "**Step1.4 Visibility Analysis**"
msgstr "**步骤1.4 可见性分析**"

#: ../../topics/system/intro.rst:80
msgid ""
"The compiler performs visibility analysis on the operator graph to "
"determine which nodes are visible to each party, and optimize the graph "
"accordingly."
msgstr "编译器在操作图上执行可见性分析以确定哪些节点对每个参与方可见，并根据需要优化图。"

#: ../../topics/system/intro.rst:82
#, fuzzy
msgid "**Step1.5 Generate Execution Graph**"
msgstr "**步骤1.5 生成执行图**"

#: ../../topics/system/intro.rst:84
#, fuzzy
msgid "The compiler generates an execution graph for the query Q."
msgstr "编译器为查询 Q 生成执行图。"

#: ../../topics/system/intro.rst:86
msgid "Execution Graph for Q"
msgstr "Q 的执行图"

#: ../../topics/system/intro.rst:89
#, fuzzy
msgid "**Step1.6 Split Execution Graph**"
msgstr "**步骤1.6 拆分执行图**"

#: ../../topics/system/intro.rst:91
msgid ""
"The compiler splits the execution graph into subgraphs based on the "
"parties of the nodes."
msgstr "编译器根据执行图上节点的拥有方将执行图拆分为子图。"

#: ../../topics/system/intro.rst:93
msgid "subgraphs"
msgstr "子图"

#: ../../topics/system/intro.rst:97
#, fuzzy
msgid "Step2. Execute on Engines"
msgstr "步骤2. 在引擎上执行"

#: ../../topics/system/intro.rst:99
msgid ""
"The subgraphs are sent to corresponding SCQLEngine nodes. SCQLEngine "
"cooperates with peer engines to execute the graph and produces the final "
"result of query Q."
msgstr "子图被发送到相应的 SCQLEngine 节点。SCQLEngine 与对等引擎协作执行图并生成查询 Q 的最终结果。"

